[SN]TITLE[SN]
World Book Day 2016: What gets you excited about books?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Lots of you will be taking part in World Book Day on Thursday, 3 March 2016.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
3 March 2016 Last updated at 07:32 GMT
It's a yearly celebration of brilliant books and reading that's been running for 19 years.
Events are taking place all over the UK and Ireland, and in over 100 countries across the world.
Ricky went along to one of them to find out why you love books.
